Source: libdevice-rfxcom-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), libanyevent-mocktcpserver-perl
Build-Depends-Indep: perl (>= 5.6.10-12)
Maintainer: Mark Hindess <soft-debian@temporalanomaly.com>
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: http://wiki.github.com/beanz/device-rfxcom-perl/

Package: libdevice-rfxcom-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libmodule-pluggable-perl
Description: Perl extension for RFXCOM RF receivers/transmitters
 This module provides an API for communicating with RFXCOM RF
 receivers and transmitters (http://www.rfxcom.com/).  It also
 provides a small wrapper for W800 receivers from WGL
 (http://www.wgldesigns.com/w800.html).
 .
 Code for RFXCOM RF transmitters will be included shortly.
